{"tid":39255,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拒奏國歌時肅立　印度12民眾國際電影節被捕","createTime":"2016-12-14T12:48:13.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T11:08:59.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1c62182c37bc03e510a4fa1b6966333ead7a36a9","tid":39255,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T12:48:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161214/photo/bknint-20161214181737801-1214_17011_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161214%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20161214181737801-1214_17011_001_01p.jpg&h=f4ad08b7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=7it%2F1bFr0qyUD3o5YqEL838C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=6df066f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】 印度最高法院於上月底裁決，戲院在電影播放前必須播放國歌，觀眾更要肅立向國旗和國歌致敬。惟最高法院並未說明違反規定後的法律責任，但各邦可自行決定當地的規範和懲罰。印度西南部日前舉行的國際電影節中，有12名民眾因拒絕在國歌演奏時肅立而被捕，觸發近百名示威者抗議。 <br />\n<br />\n喀拉拉特邦警方周一接獲國際電影節的主辦單位報案，稱有民眾在電影播放前，拒絕肅立，警員從現場拘捕多人，他們事後獲准保釋。警方透露，他們已立案調查被捕人士是否觸犯侮辱國家聲譽的法例。一旦罪成，最高可被罰款和判監3年。 <br />\n<br />\n大批示威者周二聚集在喀拉拉特邦一所戲院外，抗議有民眾因拒絕向國歌致敬被捕，他們手持寫著「在戲院播放國歌，就像貨品在超市免費出售。請不要貶低我們的國歌」的標語。有被捕人士表示，戲院經常人滿為患，一旦站起身，便會遭別人佔去座位，故逼於無奈，無法站立。有法官指出，奏國歌肅立是要表達尊重及愛國情感。 <br />\n<br />\n觀眾須向國歌肅立的措施，引起不少衝突，南部城市真奈周日有右翼分子，襲擊了8名被指沒有起立的民眾。殘障輪椅網球選手查圖維帝（Salil Chaturvedi）曾於本年10月，在果阿邦的一間戲院看戲無法起立，而遭人襲擊及辱罵。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161214/bknint-20161214181737801-1214_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161214%2Fbknint-20161214181737801-1214_17011_001.html&d=7it%2F1bFr0qyUD3o5YqEL838C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=ad41d8bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161214/bknint-20161214181737801-1214_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"635796ea920544e1985aa487610d4fa6d041e989","tid":39255,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T13:14:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b3c611bf3b27a02f9f079e5f84050e78e94334","tid":39255,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T13:59:40.000Z","msg":"垃圾國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22ed7ae53678fb74542418697868d0dfa4a189df","tid":39255,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:01:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1cd0287798d5f0f5fcca8146d484afeefb762046","tid":39255,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:03:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4577a4aab071715384ff59700f2e6389ea7b792d","tid":39255,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:19:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5560bf5bbb862d6d41ad82cd1ca2ffe23f8b5103","tid":39255,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:26:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf4817d8b9688a7ba793c9ab0952e6e183b78f00","tid":39255,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:48:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>「拒奏國歌時肅立」會有歧義<br />\n<br />\n可以係: 某人拒奏國歌，呢個時候，12人肅立起來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n垃圾記者</blockquote><br />\n奏國歌時拒肅立 咪得 一樣咁多字"},{"pid":"5ddbbf6688c062e7d6dc52985166df6adef5d05c","tid":39255,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:01:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>「拒奏國歌時肅立」會有歧義<br />\n<br />\n可以係: 某人拒奏國歌，呢個時候，12人肅立起來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n垃圾記者</blockquote><br />\n奏國歌時拒肅立 咪得 一樣咁多字</blockquote><br />\n識就唔會做妓者啦"},{"pid":"41ac7f604ef89027324d314722a927007dd0862b","tid":39255,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re